<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <style>
      /* Email styles need to be inline */
      body {
        background-color: #f8cdd6;
        color: #4d4d4d;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .header img {
        width: 150px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .content h1 {
        color: #f8cdd6;
        font-size: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #f8cdd6;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        border: none;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #e8aebc;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #7d7d7d;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="https://i.imgur.com/2vcp5Cw.png" alt="Sakura Stay Logo" style="width: 150px; height: auto;">
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Welcome to Sakura Stay!</h1>
        <p>Dear <strong><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for joining our platform! We’re excited to have you as a part of the Sakura Stay family. Whether you're staying with us for business or leisure, we strive to make your experience unforgettable.</p>
        <p>If you ever have any questions or need assistance, don’t hesitate to contact us. We're here to ensure that your stay is as comfortable and enjoyable as possible.</p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="mailto:support@sakurastay.com" class="btn">Contact Support</a>
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="http://127.0.0.1:3000/rooms/search" class="btn btn-primary">Visit our page</a>
        </p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Sakura Stay Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2024 Sakura Stay. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>123 Sakura Avenue, Blossom City</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>